personne d'incroyable.


547
00:36:53.970 --> 00:36:55.289
Stan, tu seras ici.

548
00:36:56.450 --> 00:36:58.486
Je retourne 2 km en arrière.

549
00:36:58.930 --> 00:37:00.045
Comment je filme ?

550
00:37:00.490 --> 00:37:01.479
T'inquiète.

551
00:37:01.770 --> 00:37:03.203
Je reviens direct.

552
00:37:03.690 --> 00:37:06.079
